While the {DR CV QKD protocols} are robust to the preparation noise, they {are sensitive to the detection noise, which can lead to a security break}, as we show here. Indeed, already in the limit of arbitrarily-strong modulation and perfect implementation of the protocol, when the key rate converges to the simple modification of Equation (\ref{limkrdrvs}) as:

